<plot>Balu (Arshad Warsi) is a slick but flat-broke cabdriver whose life is changed forever when he picks up an unhappy young rich man named Rahul (Chandrachur Singh) at the airport one day. Bored with his privileged but empty life, Rahul convinces Balu to switch places with him. Rahul moves into Balu's home, where he falls hard for Balu's sister, Parvati (Priya Gill). Meanwhile, Balu realizes that the manager of Rahul's successful business has been cheating him for years--and that he has an extremely attractive daughter named Pooja (Simran).</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?535731</url></doc>
